<%= render 'shared/designer-banner' %>

<section id="why-pop-designer">
  <div class="why-designer-container">
    <div class="why-designer-content">
      <h2> Why become a Designer in PoP?</h2>
      <p>PoP is the world's first platform that allows you to get paid for your contributions to the 3D printing community. Go for the hottest design requests or those most fitted to your skills. Always retaining the Intellectual Property of your designs! You will enter a blockchain guaranteed system of rewards that certifies you as the original creator.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="become-step">
  <div class="become-container">
    <div class="become-content-container mg-right-30">
      <div class="how-to-be-number">1</div>
      <div class="designer-step-content">
        <h3>Sign up!</h3>
        <p>It's free and easy to create a Designer Account on PoP. Sign up, and fill out our application form. Describe your specialties, your background and motivations and showcase your previous portfolio.<br><br>Your application will be reviewed by our team and you will be comfirmed within days.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="become-step1-img"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="become-step">
  <div class="become-container">
    <div class="become-step1-img"></div>
    <div class="become-content-container mg-left-30">
      <div class="how-to-be-number">2</div>
      <div class="designer-step-content">
        <h3>Choose your Project</h3>
        <p>Our customers will submit their requests.There are many different types of designs that our users want. Browse through our index to see the different projects our users want completed. Once you have seen a project that appeals to you, simply click the Take Project button.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="become-step">
  <div class="become-container">
    <div class="become-content-container mg-right-30">
      <div class="how-to-be-number">3</div>
      <div class="designer-step-content">
        <h3>Get Paid</h3>
        <p>After you upload your high quality 3D design and our users have recieved their desired design, you will be promptly paid.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="become-step1-img"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<% if user_signed_in? %>
  <%= render "shared/topup-sticky" %>
<% end %>
